    {
      "id": "2020-r2-phys-4",
      "number": "I-D 问4",
      "topic": "等质量物体的碰撞与摩擦停止距离",
      "topicTag": "力学·碰撞",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "摩擦水平面上，静止的小物体 A 被同质量小物体 B 碰撞。碰撞后 A、B 分别滑行距离 $L_A$、$L_B$ 后停止。A 与 B 的反发系数为 $e$，且两物体与地面的动摩擦系数相同，求 $L_A/L_B$。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{1-e}{1+e}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{1+e}{1-e}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\left(\\dfrac{1-e}{1+e}\\right)^2$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\left(\\dfrac{1+e}{1-e}\\right)^2$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2020_R2_physics/q04.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "碰撞后的速度由动量守恒和反发系数决定；随后由摩擦做功停止，滑行距离与初速度平方成正比。",
        "analysis": "设 B 碰撞前速度为 $u$。等质量一维碰撞后，$v_A=(1+e)u/2$，$v_B=(1-e)u/2$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 写出碰撞后速度",
            "content": "$$v_A=\\frac{1+e}{2}u,\\qquad v_B=\\frac{1-e}{2}u$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 用摩擦停止距离",
            "content": "$$\\mu mgL=\\frac12mv^2\\Rightarrow L\\propto v^2$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 求距离比",
            "content": "$$\\frac{L_A}{L_B}=\\left(\\frac{v_A}{v_B}\\right)^2=\\left(\\frac{1+e}{1-e}\\right)^2$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "④ $\\left(\\dfrac{1+e}{1-e}\\right)^2$",
        "correctOption": "④"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2020-r2-phys-5",
      "number": "I-E 问5",
      "topic": "单摆绕钉子完成圆周运动的条件",
      "topicTag": "力学·圆周运动",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "长为 $L$ 的轻绳悬挂小物体，从绳与竖直方向成 $60°$ 的位置静止释放。到最低点后，物体绕最低点上方距离 $r$ 的钉子做半径为 $r$ 的圆运动。若 $r$ 大于某个长度 $R$ 就不能到达钉子正上方，求 $R/L$。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$\\dfrac18$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\dfrac16$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\dfrac15$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\dfrac14$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\dfrac13$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$\\dfrac25$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2020_R2_physics/q05.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "先用能量守恒求最低点速度，再对绕钉子的最高点使用圆周运动临界条件。",
        "analysis": "释放点比最低点高 $L(1-\\cos60°)=L/2$，所以最低点 $v_0^2=gL$。绕钉子到最高点要升高 $2r$，且最高点至少满足 $v^2\\ge gr$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 最低点速度",
            "content": "$$\\frac12mv_0^2=mg\\frac{L}{2}$$\n\n$$v_0^2=gL$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 到最高点后的速度",
            "content": "$$\\frac12mv_0^2=\\frac12mv^2+mg(2r)$$\n\n$$v^2=gL-4gr$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 临界条件",
            "content": "$$gL-4gr=gr$$\n\n$$r=\\frac{L}{5}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "③ $\\dfrac{R}{L}=\\dfrac15$",
        "correctOption": "③"
      }
    },
    {
